===== Welcome to Bacon.Place's Dynamic Dns Firewall Updater =====

This software is provided without warranty of any kind, although we do our best
to ensure quality of code.

This application will parse a hosts-style, space delimetered set of ports and
modify iptable entries as needed when given hostnames have a change of address.
